g.text: This workflow predict the potential burning area when a fire occurs in the Montesinho natural park in Portugal. The user is supposed to
provide the rough coordinates where the fire was spotted and the API key for api.openweathermap.org.
In order to see the report execute the entire workflow
and then click "Open the report" button in the toolbar.
